igation Management', 'Corporate Law', 'Conveyancing', 'Commercial Transactions', 'Contract Drafting & Negotiation', 'Securities & Banking Compliance', 'Corporate Governance']), to_jsonb(ARRAY['University of Nairobi - Bachelor of Laws (LLB)', 'Kenya School of Law - Diploma in Law']), to_jsonb(ARRAY['Advocate of the High Court of Kenya', 'Notary Public', 'Commissioner for Oaths', 'Member of Law Society of Kenya']), to_jsonb(ARRAY['English', 'Swahili', 'Kikuyu'])),
